Name: Fishy
About the game: Fishy is a 3D platormer. you play as a fish very far from home . traveling through 5 worlds such as a jungle oasis to under water to the frozen tundra to inside a volcano to lastly to outer space by jumping platformers and solving puzzles. play through them all or play the stages you want with stage select. there're even pic ups to increase your score!
